thread.title: Sharon Gardiner
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Sharon Gardiner

author: Sharon Gardiner
title: Sharon Gardiner
text: I ordered genuine Brother ink for one of my printers and generic brand for the other. While there is no equal to Brother genuine ink I am very pleased with the quality of the generic ink and the ease of which the other Brother machine used it. I searched many sites and regular retail stores before purchasing from Ink Station, their prices on genuine and generic inks are very competitive. Delivery is amazingly fast. I ordered on a Saturday afternoon and the ink was at my door on Monday! Can't praise this company enough.
